metadata.description: Codex P2a shows an organic-crystalline structure and thematises the increasing blurring of the boundary between the worlds of digital images and material objects. Based on an organic elementary form that has been computerized and multiplied, the resulting structure does exhibit a naturalistic quality and tangibility, but at the same time, its claim to reality is undone and undermined by their strictly geometric and graphic surface properties.
